                    Get an instant quote.
                </p>
                <!-- <p class="xs:text-md sm:text-2xl leading-tight sm:max-w-xl max-w-3xl mb-4 mx-auto">
                    Answers in minutes.
                </p> -->

                <p class="xs:text-md sm:text-2xl leading-tight sm:max-w-xl max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-6">
                    Book online today.
                </p>

                <a href="/instant-quote/?step=1" class="btn btn-primary text-lg text-white py-2 w-64 max-w-xs mx-auto mb-4">
                    <PriceReceipt />
                    <p>Instant Quote</p>
                </a>
                <a href="tel:6165551234" class="btn btn-outline text-lg bg-white/50 text-black py-2 w-64 max-w-xs mx-auto mb-4 shadow-sm">
